        "old_string": "# CdsTranche Implementation Progress\n\n## Key Patterns Identified\n- **Joda-Beans**: All products use @BeanDefinition, ImmutableBean, Serializable\n- **CdsIndex pattern**:\n  - Base class has full fields with @PropertyDefinition\n  - Trade wrapper holds TradeInfo + Product + optional upfrontFee\n  - Resolved form has expanded payment periods\n- **Pricer pattern**: IsdaHomogenousCdsIndexProductPricer converts to ResolvedCds, uses IsdaCdsProductPricer\n- **Measure pattern**: CalculationFunction maps Measures to SingleMeasureCalculation lambdas\n\n## Implementation Files to Create\n1. `modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/credit/CdsTranche.java`\n2. `modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/credit/CdsTrancheTrade.java`\n3. `modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/credit/ResolvedCdsTranche.java`\n4. `modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/credit/IsdaCdsTranchePricer.java`\n5. `modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/credit/CdsTrancheTradeCalculationFunction.java`\n\n## CdsTranche Key Fields\n- underlyingIndex: CdsIndex\n- attachmentPoint: double (0.0-1.0)\n- detachmentPoint: double (0.0-1.0)\n- others: inherited from index (buySell, currency, notional, fixedRate, paymentSchedule)",
